name: Royal India
overview:
Escape to the hottest Indian restaurant in San Diego. At multi award winner Royal India you will be utterly pampered with gracious hospitality, plush Ambiance and world class food made with authentic ingredients and recipes, that will leave you utterly aglow.

*Serve the finest authentic Indian cuisine from “TOP CHEF” winners

  • Uses finest natural ingredients, choicest meats, seafood and fresh vegetables
  • Every dish is cooked home style, recipes from our MOM’s Indian kitchen creating Award winning menu
  • Fresh baked Nan breads made to order in our TANDOOR
  • Magnificent ambiance with large waterfall, Custom hand carved Full bar serving Indian Mojito and Mango Martinis
  • We provide sumptuous interiors with architectural designs imported from the palaces of India bringing the vibrancy of India from colonial times incorporating a palette of rich colors
  • Truly enjoyable 125 seat dining experience
  • Indian Food Banquets and catering available for all occasions
